; restart-bridge - relaunch the AmigaBridge daemon after it has been asked
; to shut down. Run DETACHED so it survives the old daemon exiting:
;   Run >NIL: Execute MEDIA1:_mcp/restart-bridge
; Waits for the old instance to release its port/IPC, then starts the new one.
Wait 4
Run >NIL: MEDIA1:_mcp/amiga-bridge TCP 2345
